===Easy===
[[File:League tasks - Easy.png|left]]
Each task in this tier awards '''10''' league points upon completion.

With {{#var_final:Asg1Count}} tasks available, there are a total of {{#var_final:Asg1Value}} league points that can be earned from easy tasks.

{{LeagueTaskHeader|collapsible=yes}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Craft an Air Rune|Craft an [[air rune]] at the [[Air Altar]].|s={{SCP|Runecraft|1|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Move Your House to Taverley|Move your [[player-owned house]] to [[Taverley]].|s={{SCP|Construction|10|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Receive a Slayer Task From Turael or Spria|Receive a [[Slayer task]] From [[Turael]] in [[Burthorpe]] or [[Spria]] in [[Draynor Village]].|s={{SCP|Slayer|1|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Defeat a Troll in Asgarnia|Defeat a [[Troll]] in [[Asgarnia]].|s=|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Defeat a Blue Dragon in Asgarnia|Defeat a [[blue dragon]] in Asgarnia.|s=|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Defeat a Black Demon in Asgarnia|Defeat a [[black demon]] in Asgarnia.|s=|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Complete the Easy Falador Diary|Complete all of the easy tasks in the [[Easy Falador Diary|Falador Achievement Diary]].|s='''See diary page'''|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Unlock a Gate in Taverley Dungeon|Unlock a gate in [[Taverley Dungeon]] using the [[dusty key]].|s=|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Enter the Taverly{{sic}} Dungeon|Enter the Taverly{{sic}} Dungeon.|s=|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Complete a Game of Novice Pest Control|Complete a game of novice [[Pest Control]].|s={{SCP|Combat|40|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskBottom|varname=Asg1|ppt=10}}

===Medium===
[[File:League tasks - Medium.png|left]]
Each task in this tier awards '''50''' league points upon completion.

With {{#var_final:Asg2Count}} tasks available, there are a total of {{#var_final:Asg2Value}} league points that can be earned from medium tasks.

