{{LeagueTaskRow|Defeat Some Animated Rune Armour|Defeat some [[Animated Rune Armour]] in the Warriors' Guild.|s=|other=Requires access to the [[Warriors' Guild]].}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Open the Crystal Chest|Open the [[crystal chest]] in [[Taverley]].|s=|other=Requires a [[crystal key]] to open}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Complete a Game of Intermediate Pest Control|Complete a game of intermediate [[Pest Control]].|s={{SCP|Combat|70|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskBottom|varname=Asg2|ppt=50}}

