{{LeagueTaskRow|Equip a Saradomin Sword|Equip a [[saradomin sword]].|s={{SCP|Attack|70|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
{{LeagueTaskRow|Equip a Piece of the Bandos Armour Set|Equip any piece of the [[Bandos armour]] set.|s={{SCP|Defence|65|link=yes|sort=yes}}|other=}}
